name: DevPill Public Good Blockchain Development Guide

metadata.name: DevPill Public Good Blockchain Development Guide 1/1000
metadata.description:
A public good blockchain development guide once emerged, builders used it to create the future of France. Moloch got slain, the world regenerated, and a new generation of software fought off humanity's darkest demons. 

Proceeds go to the continued development of this public good blockchain development guide (90%) and 10% to the artist that created the art for the NFT - Ana Rueda @
